        <p class="text-xl">The context is set, we begin with discovery. I start by asking a few questions about the vast array of attributes any one employee can have associated with them. This quickly gets out of hand as there are many, but we now know there needs to be a <abbr title="Minimum Viable Product">MVP</abbr> that we can ship first and that we should focus on that today.</p>
        <p class="text-xl">The scope of this discussion and first flow will be for a manager who is managing his employee's hours. Focusing on this flow will set the stage for what the UX and UI will roughly look like, then we can circle back around to see how an employee might handle their own hours, timesheets, punching in and out, etc. with what we come up with.</p>
